lign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> It needs to stop...</span><hr size=1> Greetings IV:<br>
<br>
I am writing you as a member from Talionis.. plz read my words with an open mind.<br>
<br>
First: I, myself, would like to appologize for my inappropriate actions wherever and whenever committed.  If they were thought inappropriate by anyone in your guild, they were at least close to being so.<br>
<br>
Second: Contrary to what I hear, I promice you I have never contacted anyone guilded and try to sway them to leave their guild in order to join mine.  I guess I'm not to popular with your people so that might not go very far, but I said it and its true.<br>
<br>
The real reason for my posting...<br>
<br>
I have asked my guild to do the same (you will see it later in post) thing that I am asking you right now.<br>
<br>
Truce please?<br>
<br>
Both of our guilds have became to hate (dislike) each other for some valid and some unreasonable reasons.  I am not trying to chalk up who did what.. cuz honestly.. I'd be here forever and to no end.. it would serve zero purpose.  Both of our guilds are doing/have done wrong things to each other.  I didnt &quot;order&quot; my guild to do anything.. simply asked them to drop the hatred, and start being profesional.  We dont have to like each other, we dont have to tagteam Sont (those were some nasty fights eh?), but we can act profesional towards each other.  We will still race for mobs, we will still FCFS each other .. yadda ya.. same as any guild would.  If we could just make sure that before we say something via ANY channel towards or about each other, we review it and decide wether or not it is constructive or destructive, and if it is the latter - throw it out.  Not just you - us too.. everyone.<br>
<br>
Please please, this is not a thread where I want anyone to repost saying but but but he did this, if you gotta ignore me cuz you think this is stupid fine.. but dont slam me please.<br>
<br>
I'm not trying to be Mr. Highandmightysavestheday guy or anything like that.  I just think we are ALL above the way we are acting (no one in particular, speaking only of he whole guilds) and all it would take to end is is... well.. simply stopping.  It will take time and work, and for some hotheads on both sides - alot of work, but it can be done muh gawtz faith in us all.<br>
<br>
If some of you think there has been to much wrong committed, to much damage done, to many bridges burnt.. to repair relationships or adjust your thinking, then I feel for you.. but I dont think thats the case here.<br>
<br>
Calonderiel<br>
Talionis<br>
<br>
This is what I asked my own guild:<br>
<br>
I am writing this post as a guildmember, not an officer. Please read it and see if we can end some needless childsplay:<br>
<br>
This whole &quot;we hate IV&quot; and IV's &quot;we hate Talionis&quot; thing has got to stop. <br>
<br>
I myself have done/said things I shouldnt have, and I will appologize on the IV boards when I write a similar post to them. Alot of us have, and still do things not in keeping with our standards of conduct that our guid is used to. Same from them, they have said and done wrong things as well. So many things have been said and done infact, that you cant even count them all or know where to start to see whos &quot;the most at blame&quot;. Whats the use? What would it accomplish if you could? .. nothing.<br>
<br>
We dont have to like each other, but can we please stop slamming each other be it ooc, shout, p.com, tells back and forth, even - in our own guildsay. Its just not healthy and theres no need for it. It would be wonderful if we could repair our relationship to them until we were back at the place where we were during the tagteam Sont era, but we all know that wont happen. Thats ok tho... all we really need to do is end the hatefullness and start the professionalism. <br>
<br>
Not trying to start a thread here where we get the &quot;well they did this to me, and untill they serve their own head on a silver jeweled platter to me I will continue to hate them&quot; type of response. If you dont agree with me thats fine .. but start your own rant thread =).<br>
<br>
Truce plz.<br>
<br>
Calonderiel <br>
